lead_paragraph: Justin Rose was still on the course and still atop the leader board when the sun went down yesterday. Rose, coming off a 12-under 60 on Thursday, was 17 under through 16 holes when the second round of the Funai Classic in Lake Buena Vista, Fla., was suspended because of darkness.
